name: The Regal Roar Exquisite India Hard Bound Notebook
description:
The Regal Roar
“The most magnificent creature in the entire world, the tiger is.” - Jack Hanna
Tigers seem so removed from our daily life – their forest homes are hundreds of kilometres away and for many of us, the only tigers we see are in photographs. The world was once home to nine subspecies of tigers. Today, only five remain – Bengal, Amur, Northern Indochinese, Malayan and Sumatran. The remaining four – Caspian, Bali, Javan and South China – are already extinct. Unfortunately, if we don’t curb our selfishness today, the only place our future generation may get to see these beautiful creatures would be in picture books.

A Doodle Collection Initiative
At Doodle Collection, apart from creating trendy diaries, we also believe in giving back to society. With that in mind, we envisioned “Exquisite India” - our effort in protecting India’s rich wildlife and culture.
This specially crafted, limited edition range of premium diaries has been illustrated by skilled artisans and rendered in a rustic golden glaze. A percentage of the sale proceeds will be sent to various NGO that has been doing commendable work in protecting endangered species.
As citizens of one of the world’s finest cultures and rich flora and fauna, we believe it is up to us to do our bit in maintaining it. And we thank you for your support towards this noble initiative that has been ignored for far too long now.

name: The Elegant Antelope Exquisite India Hard Bound Notebook
description:
The Elegant Antelope

“We are beginning to realize the almost irreparable loss in such cruel and barbaric practices as hunting and killing innocent creatures for pleasure… whose sole offence is Being Beautiful” - Joseph Goodavage
In the 19th Century, blackbucks roamed in open plains from the base of the Himalayas to the area of Cape Comorin, and from Punjab to Lower Assam. The blackbuck population is now confined to a few small pockets in North India, thanks mostly to poaching for their beautiful horns. Irrational destruction of wild plants and herbs, excessive constructions in open areas and speeding vehicles are other common reasons. Farmers viewed blackbucks as crop-raiders, further contributing to their decline. Unfortunately, if we don’t curb our selfishness today, the only place our future generation may get to see these beautiful creatures would be in picture books.

A Doodle Collection Initiative
At Doodle Collection, apart from creating trendy diaries, we also believe in giving back to society. With that in mind, we envisioned “Exquisite India” - our effort in protecting India’s rich wildlife and culture.
This specially crafted, limited edition range of premium diaries has been illustrated by skilled artisans and rendered in a rustic golden glaze. A percentage of the sale proceeds will be sent to various NGO that has been doing commendable work in protecting endangered species.
As citizens of one of the world’s finest cultures and rich flora and fauna, we believe it is up to us to do our bit in maintaining it. And we thank you for your support towards this noble initiative that has been ignored for far too long now.

name: The Spectacular Peacock Exquisite India Hard Bound Notebook
description:
The Spectacular Peacock
“The pride of the peacock is the glory of God” - William Blake
The fact says that inhuman hunting of our precious wildlife has affected the glamorous National Bird, the peacock, pushing it to the brink of extinction. Poaching for its beautiful feathers and deliberate spraying of pesticides are the most common causes of the plummeting peacock population across India. Most of the peacocks are killed during the mating season. They end up being an easier hunt since male peacocks spread open their elegant wings and dance during this time. They are also easy to track and capture, since they sleep on the same trees every night. Unfortunately, if we don’t curb our selfishness today, the only place our future generation may get to see these beautiful creatures would be in picture books.

As citizens of one of the world’s finest cultures and rich flora and fauna, we believe it is up to us to do our bit in maintaining it. And we thank you for your support towards this noble initiative that has been ignored for far too long now.

Catch me if you can, hold my hand,
Would you leave a chance at being yourself?
For the joy of writing.

description:
Fun comes in all shapes and sizes. Sometimes it comes in a slim slick package.
Whoever said enjoyment can’t be bought probably didn’t own a Color Slim notebook by Doodle.
With maddening beautiful colours like sunset orange, a calm green and a citrus yellow, these are pages to fill up with your ever-growing creativity.
Scribbling away was never this fun!

Inspired to create, unstoppable fingers,
Won’t you let them lose with indelible ink?
For the joy of writing

name: Ethnic Wave Ethnic Hard Bound Notebook
description:
It is time to blend in and yet stand out. Our cultures meet us every day. In words, in design, in art. When tradition meets chic, there’s beauty and there’s magic. Such is the magic in Doodle’s Ethnic Diary, which fuses culture with style, and design with finesse. Rich with techniques such as gold foiling and embossing, these diaries are every diary lover’s delight! So pick one, and let your ethnic styles collide into a beautiful fusion!
Cultures are meeting in handshakes warm,
Won’t you want to relive the union?
For the joy of writing.

name: Glitterati Bling Hard Bound Notebook
description:
Sparkle, shine & stardust
everything nice comes
clubbed in our pastel
masterpieces embellished
with Swarovski crystals, accompanied with a
coloured coordinated stone studded pencil.

Days go on, in their own
rhythm. Night pass by with
dark blanket. And day after
day, we live similar lives.
What can possibly change
things is a little bling, that
dash of glitter, and the
splash of sparkle! And we
have just that for you in
Doodle’s Bling Diary!
Studded with glitter and soft-hued.

Shine on you diamond,
sparkle every day, glitter every moment!

name: Tranquility Orange Mindfulness PU Leather Journal
description: In today's busy world, the need for peace and calm is growing amidst the competing demands of work and personal life. Mindfulness is a simple and powerful practice that can help you cut through the noise and reclaim tranquility, wherever you are. This Journal offers a window to mindfulness and easy activities that can be done while on the move or sitting at your desk.
short_description:
In today's busy world, the need for peace and calm is growing amidst the competing demands of work and personal life. Mindfulness is a simple and powerful practice that can help you cut through the noise and reclaim tranquility, wherever you are. This Journal offers a window to mindfulness and easy activities that can be done while on the move or sitting at your desk.

This journal is your tool and companion to a more peaceful, productive day to manage the modern world without chanting mantras or finding hours of special time to meditate.

Beautifully crafted softbound PU leather journal of 5 Booklets handstitched together with copper zari. Specially designed PU strap with a debossed design leaf which doubles up as a bookmark

This 244 pages journal includes 104 non dated ruled pages (80 gsm), 56 Weekly planner pages (80 gsm), 52 mindfulness activity pages (80 gsm) and 56 Tear-away notecard & Quote card pages (120 gsm) for every mood an occasion.

Unique handstitched binding means the pages stay firmly in place. Ideal size for easy to carry along everywhere you go! In your bagpack, handbag or bedside table

This journal comes in a beautifully printed gift box, making it an ideal gift for birthday, anniversary and working executive for a work play balance

description:
In today's busy world, the need for peace and calm is growing amidst the competing demands of work and personal life. Mindfulness is a simple and powerful practice that can help you cut through the noise and reclaim tranquility, wherever you are. This Journal offers a window to mindfulness and easy activities that can be done while on the move or sitting at your desk. This five section journal is held together with a PU debossed design on Cover. The sections comprise of, 104 ruled pages to record your thoughts, thoughtfully illustrated 25 mindfulness activities, 52 weekly planners for those who thrive on being organized, and design coordinated tear-away notecards and quirky quote cards for every mood an occasion. This journal is your tool and companion to a more peaceful, productive day to manage the modern world - without chanting mantras or finding hours of special time to meditate.

Beautifully crafted softbound PU leather journal OF 5 Booklets handstitched together with copper zari. Specially designed PU strap with a debossed design leaf which doubles up as a bookmark

This 244 pages  journal includes 104 Non dated ruled pages(80 gsm), 56 Weekly planner pages(80 gsm), 52 Activity pages(80 gsm) and 32 Tear-away notecards & Quote cards(120 gsm) .

Unique handstitched binding means the pages stay firmly in place

Ideal size for easy to carry along everywhere you go! In your bagpack,handbag or bedside table

This journal comes in a beautifully printed gift box, making it an ideal gift for birthday, anniversary and working executive for a work play balance

description:
Sparkle, shine & stardust
everything nice comes
clubbed in our pastel
masterpieces embellished
with Swarovski crystals, accompanied with a
coloured coordinated stone studded pencil.

Days go on, in their own
rhythm. Night pass by with
dark blanket. And day after
day, we live similar lives.
What can possibly change
things is a little bling, that
dash of glitter, and the
splash of sparkle! And we
have just that for you in
Doodle’s Bling Diary!
Studded with glitter and soft-hued.

Shine on you diamond,
sparkle every day, glitter every moment!

name: London Dreams City Wiro Bound Diary/Planner
description:
British tea, grandeur by the Thames, the Big Ben, the London Eye, have been drawing millions to London. The majestic museums that hold history dear, the iconic telephone booths and the lush parkland add to the charm of the city. London stands for gothic, greens and the gush of art galleries.
Doodle packs this richness in its city diaries that complete the London picture for you. With a transparent page that adds elements to the cityscape, these diaries will take you down London lanes for sure!
The Big Ben keeps time, you keep dreaming,
Won’t you paint the town red and blue?
For the joy of writing.

name: Doorway To Dubai City Wiro Bound Diary/Planner
description:
If there’s anything that describes Dubai the best, it has to be Dubai being Truly Global. It is a beautiful amalgamation of history, art, the past and a visionary future that speaks through its towering monuments, world class shopping, exhilarating adventures and bling downtown experiences.
A city that is constantly in flux can only be described the best through tiny parts that add to the whole. Doodle brings to you, city diaries that complete the Dubai picture for you. With a transparent page that adds elements to the cityscape, these diaries will take you down Dubai lanes for sure!
Soak in the souk, drench in the deserts,
Won’t you want to go truly madly global?
For the joy of writing.

Won’t you keep writing while it lasts?
For the joy of writing.

name: Bold And Brawn Executive PU Hard Bound Notebook
description:
Here's to you rebels who rebel for a cause! The cause is almost always to become the best version of you.
And while it's too easy to fit in moulds and to be what the world expects of you, it's thrilling to be yourself. Funnily enough, being yourself is true rebellion!
For those of you kicked to make it out of this world, alive, know this. There are more like you, who will one day change the world. The world will be your world.
But changing the world will need planning. A lot of it. Start writing down your brilliant ideas now!
Doodle's new men's diaries are just the right partners for this beginning!
Ruled, PU leather diaries in attractive colors, these will spark your plans to fruition!

Who's is that world, this one's mine.
Write your own story, won't you?
For the joy of writing.

description:

We men need schedules anyway but no one needs to remind us when it's time to shine! Maybe a diary can help. And not just any diary! Doodle Collection's new Men's series of diaries are for those who Dream big and work bigger!
PU leather, ruled diaries, these are the perfect schedulers! Grab one already!

Tick tock tick tock,
The clock strikes a win!
Won't you write that success too?
For the joy of writing.

name: Ivory Ethnic Soft Bound Center Stitch Diary/Planner
description:
An art from the epics, it swirls and swells at the ends. The enthralling beauty in the free-hand work has had patronage and legacy. Kalamkari, an art long forgotten and now found has found its way to Doodle diaries. Block prints to imprint on your mind forever, these are diaries to keep and cherish. The intricate work, the finer details, the grandeur of it all!
Doodle brings Kalamkari back in vogue with its Slim range of notebooks. These are head-turners for sure, so you need to get your hands on these ethereal beauties!
It’s one thing to dwell in art, another to own it.
Own a legacy, rich craftsmanship, won’t you?
For the joy of writing.

I for identity, I for initials,
Etch your name in every heart,
For the joy of writing.

Our lives revolve around making a name, a life, our identities. It's essential for our lives, to have our names etched into people's hearts. Do it with Doodle's all new collection of Initial diaries! Your name starts with U? You have your own diary, with a gorgeous cut out of the initial onto the outer cover and a soothing pastel and attractive flowery pattern on it. It speaks of you and you alone. What about your friend who's name starts with P? She can have her own! I for identity, I for initials, Etch your name in every heart, For the joy of writing.

description: People all around the world are doing epic shit! No, seriously, they are! And they have epic people all around! That’s true, well, so be epic and stay surrounded by these crazy, mad insane people who drive you to do those unimaginable things! Like driving to someplace at 3 o’ clock at night just to watch the city like never before, or waking you up in the middle of the night to have a spoonful of the sinful pastry sitting inside the refrigerator. And it all definitely should be written into Doodle Collection’s all new creatively crafted colourful diaries! These are the Epic Shit you’ve been waiting for! Paper-based hard bound ruled diaries, with bookmarks that you could tear out from the back folded cover inside. They are crazy, they are creative and they are mad! Just like you! That was wow, that was wonderful, just epic! Inspiring and how, stay like that forever, won’t you? For the joy of writing.

name: Old School Tween Collection Hard Bound Notebook
description: Hey there, Mr Old School. Hello, Miss Old School. You like it like the 70s don’t you? Disco, funk, smooth jazz, jazz fusion, must have your feet tapping already! Star Wars fans, a show of hands please. And David Bowie, anyone? And what about notebooks, diaries, paper? With both my hands in the air, let me tell you about this 1970s style laptop. It is something that can’t be typed into, it has to be written into. For all the digital generation, this is something that might not give you last seens or statuses. But it is sure to give you love letters, greetings and the smell of ink. Aah! Doodle Collection too has stocked up on this 1970’s style laptop. Paper-based hard bound diaries with a little special something! A bookmark that you can tear off from the back inside cover, really! So old school, that oh-so-amazing smell, Nothing beats that feeling of the pages. For the joy of writing.

name: Story Teller Tween Collection Hard Bound Notebook
description:
What makes the best stories? Routine? Nah! Travel escapades, train journeys? Not always! Successes? Nah! Failures? Yes. Bad choices? Yes. Bad decisions?
Yes, yes, yes. The best stories often arise from the worst worst worst decisions. Why? Because they are just so interesting, so full of drama, the ups and downs, the hiccups, and you’ve gotta agree we love these hiccups. That little jump on the hardest hiccups, on the worst roads. Cool stories are often inspired by some not-so-cool events. Some things we write in our diaries, only late at night, and then we hide the diary under our pillows.
Doodle Collection has some really new cool diaries, which you can fill up with your crazy life stories! Paper based hard bound diaries with ruled pages, these diaries do have something cooler about them! You can tear out a bookmark from the back folded cover inside. Cool, innit?

Good bad or the ugly, choose,
Only the bad ones make cool tales to tell.
For the joy of writing.

name: Nick of Time Tween Collection Hard Bound Notebook
description: 100 days to go, no motivation. 50 days to go, nah, none yet. 20 days to go, maybe you’ll get up from the couch and shake off the rust. 10 days, maybe a long-pending shower, and some fresh smelling clothes. 5 days to go, aah, now that’s a good reason to get up and open the books. What subject is it anyway? 1 day to go, let’s get some coffee now, the night is long and I’m super productive! Be is exams, assignments, or even a client presentation, isn’t it what we all are guilty of doing? Now you need some notebooks, right? We have you covered. Doodle’s new range of diaries and notebooks for those Last minute kings and queens of the arena! Gear up, pull your socks up and write all night into these paper based, hard bound ruled diaries, with a bookmark that you can tear off from the back inside cover! What time is it, it’s my time, The last minute champion of everything, For the joy of writing.

A meaow, a purr, and some scratching and clawing, Won’t you pour some feline love onto paper? For the joy of writing.

name: Ink Story Tween Collection Wiro Hard Bound Notebook
description:
Screens, so many of them. We are addicted to these screens, burning bright in front of our eyes, turning us blind to the treasure that books are. Writing, the long lost art of letter writing or even poetry. We are engaged all day long, relentlessly typing into our mobile phones, our tablets, our laptops. But what happened to writing with in pens onto crisp white paper? The pleasure of turning a page over and of finding a blank new canvas to pour onto! 
Don’t you worry, Doodle’s new diaries are so inspiring, you’ll want to sit with it and an ink pen and forget the world, we promise! Wired, Paper based hard bound diaries with ruled pages; these are perfect diaries to resume you long lost writing habits with! 

Fingers on keys or pen onto paper?

Walk the road less travelled,
And rediscover yourself,
For the joy of writing.

categories: Doodle Menu/DIARIES & NOTEBOOKS,Doodle Menu/Sale,Doodle Menu/DIARIES & NOTEBOOKS/Lifestyle Notebooks/Mindfulness
name: Doodle Mindfulness Planner
description:
The present is a present, a gift, and we should learn to embrace it, love it and be in it. The past and the future hold things we cannot control. Only the present can be tamed, changed and acted upon. Mindfulness is a lifestyle. Once in a while, it is great to be by yourself and enjoy your own company. And this includes, reading books, watching movies, going on walks, long drives, solving a puzzle with a cup of coffee, or just watching the rain. It can almost be like meditation. In this hurried, hectic life, all that we crave for is some solitude, some peace and some time to relax; leisure is the word. And Doodle Collection is the place, if you are looking for planners to help you in your Mindfulness journey. It is full of surprises on every page, along with ruled planner pages. To do lists, goals, ambition, you can fill it all, it is a self evaluation process after all. Fill it up with your colourful thoughts, black and white feelings on gloomy days and just fill in pixels on the rest of the days when you feel like meh. 

This Mindfulness planner is paper based with print and foil on the cover! Really an attractive way to stay mindful, we say! The moment is now, the present is here, Hold on with both your hands, will you? For the joy of writing.

name: Love Confessions Notebook
description:
COVER STRUCTURE AND FEEL: This journal is styled with spot UV lettering at the front and a diagonal checkered design on the front and back cover.

ADDS-ONS: This notebook is styled with a customized, heart-shaped PU dangler that can also be used as a bookmark to make sure that you can pick up where you left off. This diary also has a page with a photo frame and one with 10 tear-away love coupons.

EASY TO WRITE AND TEAR: Constructed with a s top wiro binding, this paper-based journal lays flat so you can write without any trouble, no matter where you are. This softbound notebook has rounded edges that add finesse to its look.

PAGES AND RULING: This dateless journal comes with 160 ruled pages (6.5 x 8.5 inches) for you to fill with your love story.

IDEAL FOR: It is a perfect gift for your loveone,Girlfriend,Best Friend,Boy Friend, Birthday Gift, Valentine's Day. Express your love with Doodle Diaries
short_description:
Are you someone who believes in loving someone from afar or do you think that one should confess their love no matter what the outcome? If you are the latter, you would certainly love the ‘Love Confessions’ diary by Doodle Collections. Inscribed with the words ‘I can Never Find the Words that Say How Much I Love You’ in spot UV, this paper-based, softbound diary describes the essence of true love. If you feel the same way about someone, gift them this diary and let the words do the talking for you.
This love journal is further enhanced with scenic end pages and 3 little hearts at the top of each of the 160 ruled pages. When you feel like putting your feelings on paper, you can use the ruled insert page with scattered red hearts at the top and bottom. When you want to get a little more romantic, opt for one of the 4 pre-filled tear-away love coupons or get more creative and use one of the 6 empty ones and hand them over to your partner, which they can use whenever they want a movie night, a big cuddle, or anything else that you have promised them. What’s more, this diary comes with an insert page that has a photo frame with 2 cute hearts at the bottom where you can stick your favorite photo of the two of you. All this and more makes this notebook a thoughtful and romantic gift.

COVER STRUCTURE AND FEEL: The front and back cover is styled with randomly placed colorful hearts and the front cover also features multicolor spot UV lettering.

EASY TO WRITE AND TEAR: Constructed with a s top wiro binding, this paper-based journal lays flat so you can write without any trouble, no matter where you are. This softbound notebook has rounded edges that add finesse to its look.

PAGES AND RULING: This dateless journal comes with 160 ruled pages (6.5 x 8.5 inches) for you to fill with your love story.

ADDS-ONS: This notebook is styled with a customized, theme-based PU dangler that can also be used as a bookmark to make sure that you can pick up where you left off. This diary also has a page with a photo frame and one with 10 tear-away love coupons.

IDEAL FOR: It is a perfect gift for your loveone,Girlfriend,Best Friend,Boy Friend, Birthday Gift, Valentine's Day. Express your love with Doodle Diaries
short_description:
Are you in love? Does your partner make you happy? If so, it is your onus to make them feel the same way. You can show how much you love your bae by gifting them the ‘Happy in Love’ diary by Doodle Collection.
This diary can make for a perfect love journal that can be the testament of your relationship. You can write a love letter to your partner on the ruled insert page with scattered red hearts at the top and bottom. This diary also has 4 pre-filled and 6 empty tear-away love coupons that you can gift each other and cash in every now and then to keep the romance alive. But what’s a love journal without pictures, right? Don’t worry we have you covered. This softbound notebook has a photo frame stuck to an insert page with 2 cute hearts at the bottom. This diary also has a personalized, theme-based PU dangler that can be engraved with your partner’s name.

Designed with randomly placed hearts at the front and back cover and colorful spot UV lettering at the front, this notebook will make an ideal gift, be it Valentine’s day or any other day that celebrates your love.

short_description:
When you love someone with all your heart, you want to give them everything in the world. But what is more special than the most expensive gift? A gift that was especially made for your partner. If your husband, wife, girlfriend or boyfriend loves you and loves everything about your relationship, they will certainly love the ‘Forever Mine’ diary by Doodle Collection.
This notebook is styled with a colorful spot UV design and lettering on the front cover. There are 3 uniquely designed inserts that can help you express your love. short_description: Being in love is the best feeling in the world. The butterflies in the stomach, the blushing cheeks, the love-filled eyes, every experience in love is special. And the one emotion that we feel constantly, is happiness. When you are in love, nothing or no one can make you unhappy. The colors seem brighter, the sounds seem sweeter and the world just seems like a better place. It is true, one person can certainly make the world a better place for you. If you know someone who does the same for you, show them your love and tell them that they make you happy, even when the skies are grey. Styled with spot UV typography at the front cover, and randomly placed hearts at the front and back, this notebook will certainly make for a quirky addition in their stationery collection. Constructed with an exposed sewn binding, this hardbound diary has strategically placed colored page inserts that give the spine a gorgeous multicolor look. The 24 inserts include some love quotes that help you express how you feel, a page where you can note down all your special days, one that reminds you to do things for yourself, a page that makes you list down your favorite books, and one that asks you what your favorite movies are, among others. short_description: What is life without love and laughter? Don’t you just love long drives on an endless road, into the horizon, with your significant other? The endless conversations and the laughter that just does not stop? Sounds like a perfect date, doesn’t it? Life should be full of these small moments filled with love that make it magical. The ‘Love and Laughter’ dairy by Doodle Collection is our small way of reminding you to do these things and keep the magic alive. This paper-based diary has an exposed sewn binding construction and strategically placed colored page inserts that give the spine a gorgeous multicolor look. To keep you inspired and to help you express your love, this diary is designed with some beautiful and some random love quotes. Other than the quotes, there are colored inserts like the page where you can list down your favorite books and one where you can write down your favorite movies. There’s also a page for you to doodle on and one for you to pen down the most magical moments of the year. short_description:
Doesn’t it happen sometimes that you meet someone and feel like they are all you were looking for all your life? Like they just seamlessly fit in every part of your life? Like they perfectly complement you? Like they were the frosting to your cupcake, the dip to your chips, and cheese to your macaroni? Well, the ‘Perfect Match’ dairy has been designed for you. Yes, your love has inspired us to make a diary that you will love.
Made to be your love journal, this hardbound diary features 24 colored inserts from pages to pen down your favorite movies, book, and memories, to pages that remind you to love yourself and your partner. There’s also a page where you can write down all your many anniversaries so none of you forget to celebrate the special day. Designed with quirky love quotes like ‘Forever is a long time, but I wouldn’t mind spending it by your side’ and ‘Wouldn’t it be a perfect crime, if I stole your heart and you stole mine?’, this notebook is the epitome of romantic love. The little cherry on the top of this love cake is the exposed sewn binding construction and strategically placed colored page inserts that give the spine a gorgeous multicolor look.

short_description:
You will always be my forever.’ This line defines a love that is very rare; a love that stays no matter what; a love that defies all the rules of society; a love that makes who feel weak in the knees and strong in the mind. If you have found that love or are looking for it, the ‘Together Forever’ diary from Doodle Collection is the perfect match for you.
This diary is designed with 168 ruled pages that have 3 tiny hearts at the top so you can write about your aspirations and your affirmations. The colored inserts like love quotes provide inspiration, while some others remind you to enjoy the little things. While some let you pen down your favorites, some others let you doodle to your heart’s content. These colored sections along with the exposed sewn binding construction give the spine a beautiful, colorful look. This paper-based journal features spot UV typography and random colorful hearts on the front cover, light bulbs with tiny hearts at the back, and cute yellow, green and blue hearts on the end pages. It lies flat so you can write without any trouble, no matter where you are. This notebook also comes with tear-away tags that you can write love notes on and hand over to your loved one.

name: Hopeless Romantic Notebook
description:
COVER STRUCTURE AND FEEL: This dateless diary features spot UV lettering at the front and an abstract design on the front and back cover.

ADDS-ONS: This notebook is styled with a customized, heart-shaped PU dangler that can also be used as a bookmark to make sure that you can pick up where you left off. This diary also has a page with a photo frame and one with 10 tear-away love coupons.

EASY TO WRITE AND TEAR: Constructed with a s top wiro binding, this paper-based journal lays flat so you can write without any trouble, no matter where you are. This softbound notebook has rounded edges that add finesse to its look.

PAGES AND RULING: This dateless journal comes with 160 ruled pages (6.5 x 8.5 inches) for you to fill with your love story.

IDEAL FOR: It is a perfect gift for your loveone,Girlfriend,Best Friend,Boy Friend, Birthday Gift, Valentine's Day. Express your love with Doodle Diaries
short_description:
Do you smile looking at your phone while you are walking and texting with your boo and suddenly realize you have been grinning like a fool while every passerby looked on? Do you break into song and dance in your mind every time you think of your special someone? Have you been caught day dreaming at work more than once in a day? If you can relate to any or many of these statements, you my friend are a hopeless romantic, and we have created a diary to pay homage to all love-struck humans like you.
Designed with a quirky and romantic front cover, this diary features spot UV lettering at the front and an abstract design on the front and back cover. You can document every important aspect of your relationship in this love journal. You can use the ruled insert page with scattered red hearts at the top and bottom to write a love letter to your partner and express how much they mean to you. You can exchange the 4 pre-filled and 6 empty tear-away love coupons and cash them in whenever you feel like you are having a dull day. But what’s a love journal without pictures, right? Don’t worry, this softbound notebook comes with an insert page that has a photo frame with 2 cute hearts at the bottom. Apart from these pages, this paper-based notebook has 160 ruled pages with a 3-heart design at the top of each page.
This journal checks off all the boxes of an ideal romantic gift, whether it is for Valentine’s Day, your love anniversary, or any other special day.

categories: Doodle Menu/New Arrivals
name: Bookworm Notebook
description:
COVER STRUCTURE AND FEEL: This diary features a graphic of books on the front and the back cover. Also, the front cover has a book shelf print and some spot UV lettering and books.

ADDS-ONS: This notebook is styled with a theme-based dangler that can also be used as a bookmark to make sure that you can pick up where you left off.

EASY TO WRITE AND TEAR: It's a hard bound journal with stop-wiro binding and round edges , making it easy to open flat and write comfortably as well as tearing pages neatly.

PAGES AND RULING: This dateless journal comes with 160 ruled A5 pages for you to fill with your aspirations.

IDEAL FOR: This notebook is designed to share our love of books with you. Buy it for yourself or gift it to someone who enjoys books as much as we do on women’s day, friendship’s day, their anniversary, their birthday, or any other day you choose to make special.
short_description:
Books make you travel through different places, countries and worlds, all while sitting in the reading nook of your home. A book is not only about the writer, but also about the reader because the writer can write what they want you to see, but at the end, it is your imagination that makes the story come to life. In this world full of technology, if you feel happy when you smell a new book, if you cannot go to sleep without knowing what happens next, if the most-precious gadget you own is an e-reader, you my friend are a bookworm.
To celebrate our love for books and to celebrate yours, Doodle Collection has launched the Bookworm notebook. Featuring some spot UV lettering and books on the front, and a graphic of books on the front and the back cover, this journal captures the true essence of a book lover, because you can actually never have too many books. It also comes with a theme-based dangler.

name: Buzzed Notebook
description:
COVER STRUCTURE AND FEEL: The front cover has text that is highlighted with spot UV and there are also randomly placed colorful letters on the front and the back cover.

ADDS-ONS: This notebook is styled with a theme-based dangler that can also be used as a bookmark to make sure that you can pick up where you left off.

EASY TO WRITE AND TEAR: It's a hard bound journal with stop-wiro binding and round edges , making it easy to open flat and write comfortably as well as tearing pages neatly.

IDEAL FOR: This is the perfect gift for someone who loves writing. You can buy it for yourself or gift it to someone on their birthday, friendship’s day, writer, readers or even without any special occasion.
short_description:
They say creativity flows when you are high, but what’s the guarantee of the work being error free? Well, here’s the solution. ‘Write Drunk, Edit Sober.’ And while you are at it, why not write in the Buzzed notebook. This ruled journal comes with a stop wiro binding gives your writing flexibility, whether you are sober or not, as it lays flat.
Along with randomly placed colorful letters on the front and the back cover, this diary also features spot UV lettering on the front that makes the words pop. To take the design to the next level, the Buzzed notebook comes with a theme-based dangler that can also be used as a bookmark to make sure that you can pick up where you left off.

This dateless journal is styled with a front cover that has an image of a coffee cup and highlighted spot UV lettering and it comes with 160 ruled A5 pages and a theme-based paper dangler.

name: Bucket List Notebook
description:
COVER STRUCTURE AND FEEL: This diary is styled with a blind deboss and silver foil at the front that gives it a stylish appeal.

FLEXIBLE SOFT BOUND COVER: Designed with a soft PU front and back with rounded edges, the Bucket List notebook provides the required flexibility.

PAGES AND RULING: This dateless journal comes with 160 ruled A5 pages that you can fill with your secrets and dreams.

IDEAL FOR: Made for the one who enjoys travelling, likes to plan and loves to write, this diary is the best gift for any occasion like an anniversary, a birthday, friendship’s day, or any random day that you choose to make special.
short_description:
Life is too short to spend to in a cubicle. So make sure you spend a considerable amount of it going to places, seeing people and doing things. Travel a lot because it broadens your horizons. Meeting new people and experiencing new things makes you question your beliefs and alter your perceptions. Gift the Bucket List notebook to someone who lives by this philosophy or buy it for yourself if it is true for you.
Designed with a soft bound PU cover and 160 ruled A5 pages, this dateless journal has enough space for you to pen down all the things you want to do before you are too old to do anything. The front cover of this travel diary is styled with a blind deboss all over which brings out the silver foil text that inspires you to ‘Go, See, Do.’

categories: Doodle Menu/New Arrivals,Doodle Menu/Trending Products,Doodle Menu/DIARIES & NOTEBOOKS/Lifestyle Notebooks/Glam
name: Imperfectly Perfect Notebook
description:
COVER STRUCTURE AND FEEL: This diary features deboss and silver foil styling on the front and back cover.

ADDS-ONS: This notebook is styled with a printed elastic band that wraps around the book vertically and is held in place by two metal rivets at the back.

EASY TO WRITE AND TEAR: It's a hard bound journal with a stop-wiro binding and rounded edges for a finished look. This diary can lay flat.

PAGES AND RULING: This dateless journal comes with 160 ruled A5 pages that you can fill with your shopping list, school notes, poems, or anything under the sun.

IDEAL FOR: Buy it for yourself or gift it to someone on friendship’s day, women’s day, their anniversary, their birthday, or any other day you choose to make special.
short_description:
Perfection is an unattainable concept as it is very perceptive. What will be beautiful to one, might disgust another. So don’t fall for these pre-conceived ideas of pretty and simply be your kind of beautiful. Celebrate your womanhood, let your hair down and embrace your inner goofy goddess.
Designed for the simple and straightforward woman, this PU journal has a random deboss and silver foil layout on the front as well as the back. It is styled with a printed elastic band that wraps around the book vertically and is held in place by two metal rivets at the back. Constructed with a stop wiro binding, this dateless diary lays flat and provides writing convenience no matter where your day takes you.

name: Floral Palette Notebook
description:
COVER STRUCTURE AND FEEL: The front and back cover has a floral pattern that continues inside onto the end pages.

STURDY HARD COVER BUILT TO LAST: It's a hard bound journal with a metal frame and rounded edges for a finished look.

PAGES AND RULING: This dateless journal comes with 192 ruled A5 pages for you to fill with your aspirations.

ADDS-ONS: The Floral Palette notebook comes with a theme-based dangler.

IDEAL FOR: This is the made for the woman who loves putting her feelings on paper. It is the best gift for an anniversary, a birthday, women’s day or when you simply feel like appreciating the woman in your life, because she deserves it.
short_description:
Imagine yourself sitting on fresh green grass surrounded by colorful flowers with a beautiful view of the mountains. Wouldn’t that inspire you to write? We have tried to bring a little bit of this visual to you with our Floral Palette notebook so you feel inspired to write wherever you are.
The floral design on the front and back of this hardcover diary continues inside onto the end pages. This metal frame diary comes with 192 ruled A5 pages that you can write, draw or doodle on. Adding a touch of style to this already glamorous journal is a copper metal frame and a theme-based dangler.

categories: Doodle Menu/DIARIES & NOTEBOOKS/Lifestyle Notebooks/Quirky,Doodle Menu/New Arrivals,Doodle Menu/Trending Products
name: Rumble Ruckus Notebook
description:
COVER STRUCTURE AND FEEL: This diary features deboss and color deboss styling on the front and back cover.

ADDS-ONS: This notebook is styled with a printed elastic band that wraps around the book vertically and is held in place by two metal rivets at the back.

EASY TO WRITE AND TEAR: It's a hard bound journal with a stop-wiro binding and rounded edges for a finished look. This diary can lay flat.

PAGES AND RULING: This dateless journal comes with 160 ruled A5 pages that you can fill with your shopping list, school notes, poems, or anything under the sun.

ADDS-ONS: This notebook is styled with a white printed elastic band that wraps around the book vertically and is held in place by two metal rivets at the back.
short_description:
There are three kinds of travelers. One who visits the most-popular places in the world, one who visits the most unexplored places in the world, and the third who visits all of these places from the comfort of their workstation. If you fall in the last category, the Rumble Ruckus notebook is meant exactly for you.
Styled with color foil and deboss on the front cover, this PU journal has a very trendy design. The printed elastic band that wraps around it vertically adds a touch of style. This dateless journal lays flat and comes with 160 ruled A5 pages so you have enough space and convenience to write about absolutely anything, absolutely anywhere.

name: Unicorn Notebook
description:
COVER STRUCTURE AND FEEL: The front cover has a silver foil and spot UV text.

ADDS-ONS: This notebook is styled with a theme-based dangler that can also be used as a bookmark to make sure that you can pick up where you left off.

EASY TO WRITE AND TEAR: It's a hard bound journal with stop-wiro binding and round edges , making it easy to open flat and write comfortably as well as tearing pages neatly.

PAGES AND RULING: This dateless journal comes with 160 ruled A5 pages for you to fill with your aspirations.

IDEAL FOR: This is the perfect gift for someone who is as unique as a unicorn. Buy it for yourself or gift it to someone on women’s day, friendship’s day, their anniversary, their birthday, or any other day you choose to make special.
short_description:
Be a unicorn, because why not? Unicorns are like the most sacred creature of this generation. Though it was originally supposed to be a beast, but come on, have you looked at one, in pictures of course? They are the prettiest little things, with their one horn and colorful and glitter-filled bodies. Who wouldn’t want to be one? So be a Unicorn and be Unique.
The Unicorn notebook by Doodle Collection captures the spirit of being a unicorn and is styled with a silver foil and spot UV text on the front cover. The front and back covers are also enhanced with a pastel coloured background and randomly scattered twinkling stars. Additionally, this ruled journal comes with a theme-based dangler that adds both style and convenience.

name: Book Blossoms Lite Paper Set Center Stich Soft Bound + Paper Finish Notebook
description: "Imagine this. You walk into a house, the door opens and then you walk straight into heaven. A garden full of blossoms and blooms, creepers and vines, breeze and butterflies. Now that’s a piece of haven we all want, isn’t it? The greens calm us, the scent of the flowers delights us and we get transported to this whole new world where things only grow, bloom and blossom. We could give you this piece of heaven in Doodle’s new set of three diaries. Its floral theme is so enchanting; you’ll get lost in the vines and happily entangled in the creepers. The set of three diaries are all of different sizes and have ruled pages to pour those thoughts into. Pick a green of the trees, Or the blue of the sky, won’t you? For the joy of writing. "
